-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

| Feature      | `throw`                   | `throws`               |
| ------------ | ------------------------- | ---------------------- |
| Purpose      | Actually throws exception | Declares exception     |
| Used in      | Inside method             | Method signature       |
| Type         | Followed by object        | Followed by class name |
| Number       | One exception at a time   | Multiple allowed       |
| Keyword role | Action                    | Information            |
